This paper deals with sentiment analysis using natural language processing techniques, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models such as LSTM, which is a popular topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of feature engineering and optimization techniques, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
